data.description: Enjoy having everything you need on one level in a quiet cul-de-sac. Come see this 4BR/3BA traditional ranch home in Bridgegate Estates. Neutral color scheme, separate living room transitions right into large breakfast area flanked by large open kitchen and spacious window-wrapped den with fireplace. The kitchen has a walk-in pantry and ample cabinets for lots of storage. This home has a separate designated laundry room and a wooded rear view. The primary bedroom has a large walk-in closet, vaulted ceiling, and a newly remodeled ensuite with separate sinks, spa-like corner tub, and stand-alone shower. Enjoy the large yard backed with mature trees. The 4-car parking pad offers convenient parking solutions. The home is close to downtown Graham and Burlington, shopping, and major highways. Kitchen appliances convey. Priced to sell.
